{"tid":782144,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"去海外聖上的皇宮面聖 旅行中遇到嘅貓貓","createTime":"2018-08-16T13:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T16:22:04.000Z","uid":86948,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"270609ba13af3d3532f5b520b6d2a82c4df63958","tid":782144,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"(諗左好耐開旅遊台定寵物台好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣好鍾意去旅行又好鍾意去影喵?<br />\n<br />\n愛貓國家黎計日本同土耳其都好出名<br />\n鍾意去旅行嘅我，同時亦好鍾意貓貓狗狗，所以每次去開日本如果順路又有時間的話都會去貓島去探下D貓貓<br />\n佢地有好多係放養貓，亦有好多係浪浪<br />\n由於屋企問題唔養得貓，所以唯有去旅行時同佢地玩下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為唔係旅遊台，以下唔會講得太詳細<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/201009_dd77417a41193f7abc9bcbd7773040c6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F201009_dd77417a41193f7abc9bcbd7773040c6.JPG&h=c417c388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/201037_985ec06a4b182e9a2605aabed133afdf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F201037_985ec06a4b182e9a2605aabed133afdf.JPG&h=9811c43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/201107_fd4062125a8f27a352f963d45ebc5a16.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F201107_fd4062125a8f27a352f963d45ebc5a16.JPG&h=3727b88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2Mw8246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Mw8246&h=a353ae35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2017 6月 青島</ins><br />\n青島出名係日本第一貓島，島上面住左過百隻貓貓，但係居民就只有十幾人。<br />\n島上面冇任何嘅自販機、住宿等等。同時一日只有兩往復嘅船。所以要去的話記得查清楚資料先好去呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/203227_7e39b87901dd2f3020cb64c9b208be6b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F203227_7e39b87901dd2f3020cb64c9b208be6b.JPG&h=4425fc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/203312_8496351c4f7fcd01463b9ecf8e43fe97.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F203312_8496351c4f7fcd01463b9ecf8e43fe97.JPG&h=dac070df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2017 7月 妻籠宿</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2KX9UOo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KX9UOo&h=7b9e02e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2KX9XK4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KX9XK4&h=2e8c3f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2017 12月 京都市</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2KXa3Bq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KXa3Bq&h=fd5fad6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2MTvR2O\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MTvR2O&h=511dd048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2nJIfHm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nJIfHm&h=fbc942ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2vIgSSH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vIgSSH&h=29b78826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://bit.ly/2KXttGg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KXttGg&h=6776a3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2nHfyuX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nHfyuX&h=ecddc80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2018 2月 藍島</ins><br />\n藍島亦係出名嘅貓島，同上面提及青島差不多，居民好少，一日兩往復。島上相對居民多少少，但係買野都係相當唔方便，如果要去都係查清楚資料同埋買定飲品先好去，唔好渴死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2PeZuNj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PeZuNj&h=fc8f1229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2w9ONDc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2w9ONDc&h=747508e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2vL479I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vL479I&h=8b3130ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205004_2d00b6de2c881dd2e6bc874d116547b4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205004_2d00b6de2c881dd2e6bc874d116547b4.JPG&h=144fcdf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205016_4cb7e67dfc4c489c91b8ae412d5d0354.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205016_4cb7e67dfc4c489c91b8ae412d5d0354.JPG&h=eda7fc4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2018 7月 江之島</ins><br />\n江之島其實都係出名嘅貓島，同時係好多香港人去嘅&quot;東京近郊&quot;<br />\n根據同島上一位住附近嘅愛貓姨姨講，佢話近年江之島嘅貓貓數量唔知點解開始減少。而依度嘅貓貓其實有好多都係來自日本各地嘅棄貓，變成咗浪浪。好彩有島民接濟，所以D浪浪先可以繼續生存落去，有D甚至會變成島民嘅放養貓。希望佢地未來會有安穩嘅生活啦。如果大家去開的話見到有D鐵箱喺路上寫住係比島上貓貓的話，不妨擺低少少錢，幫助下佢地啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205541_8c9f9392a073f4c33fc122fdcbf13d21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205541_8c9f9392a073f4c33fc122fdcbf13d21.jpg&h=8ccce1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205549_ce418247f70e73190a9985a6f198d1a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205549_ce418247f70e73190a9985a6f198d1a8.jpg&h=f745c33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205550_4863b04bb316d3fa3e422d92b8f4213d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205550_4863b04bb316d3fa3e422d92b8f4213d.jpg&h=a73349a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2018 7月 箱根</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/205601_7473dfbd83d43449132c3131c358f659.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F205601_7473dfbd83d43449132c3131c358f659.JPG&h=d0c12019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>2018 7月 金沢</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次唔知幾時先有機會去旅行。<br />\n希望有機會可以去下土耳其啦，聽聞 Istanbul 都好多貓貓<br />\n有冇巴絲去過其它地方影咗D貓貓大家一齊分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724d2fc62b09e8fa13ac0ba11d45bf0c2056bbe2","tid":782144,"uid":41915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"沖繩有無"},{"pid":"bad8dd837d8fc98bd84ad2c4c7f34ef66481e956","tid":782144,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"貓島啲貓咁健康嘅？聽講台灣嗰邊有啲有傳染病"},{"pid":"5021933807c4b923a4e931dc813fdc5f81094e32","tid":782144,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖繩有無</blockquote><br />\n冇去過琉球呀答你唔到<br />\n以我所知好似冇貓島"},{"pid":"aaf72a12742b88506b8b4574e1c880c7595cf36b","tid":782144,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓島啲貓咁健康嘅？聽講台灣嗰邊有啲有傳染病</blockquote><br />\n間中會有人去幫佢地檢查嫁 (好似係)"}]}